<span id="freeTextContainer5300724647909240021">Oh wow. Well I just flew through this. I can&apos;t not give it 5 stars because it kept me hooked and horrified at every turn. The ending had me gasping, for something that was SO obvious and critical to the Dollanganger novels, it didn&apos;t even occur to me until I read it at the last page. <br/>I love VC Andrews books, they just flow so easily. This one had everything, and I definitely even feel haunted now after I&apos;ve closed the book. </span>
